<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>ZeroHunger | Feeding the Deprived</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 100px; 
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 36px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 400px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            flex-basis: 25%;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .card h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
                margin-top: 0;
            }

            .card p {
                line-height: 1.5;
            }

            .card a {
                display: inline-block;
                background-color: #f00;
                color: #fff;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                text-decoration: none;
                margin-top: 10px;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>ZeroHunger</h1>
        <p>Feeding the Deprived</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>We are on a mission to reduce food waste and feed the deprived people and children in Dhaka city. Through our system, we can automate and track our work to make sure that the donated food is collected and distributed effectively.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Our Partners</h2>
            <p>We work with several restaurants in Dhaka city who donate their leftover food before it goes to waste. We collect the food and distribute it to the people who need it most.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Get Involved</h2>
            <p>If you want to join our cause or have any questions, please contact us or join now. Together we can make a difference!</p>
            <a href="Login/Signup">Join Now</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
